# Pin line-ending-sensitive checked-in artifacts to LF so worktree/clone
# checkouts under core.autocrlf=true do not materialize CRLF and break tests:
#  - server/content/generated/models.json: CRLF inflates size past the 3 MiB
#    budget asserted by tests/logh7-mdx-transform-catalog.test.mjs.
#  - tools/patch/exe-patch.mjs: tests/exe-patch.test.mjs parses this source as
#    text and matches an LF-only ('\n}\n') delimiter.
server/content/generated/models.json text eol=lf
tools/patch/exe-patch.mjs text eol=lf
